'''朱金泰'''（{{bd|？||}}），中國当代作家，独立学者，[[篆刻家|篆刻家]]。先后做过报刊[[记者|记者]]、[[主编|主编]]、[[电视|电视]][[导演|导演]]、[[制片人|制片人]]<ref>[http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=2&CurRec=2&dbcode=CJFD&dbname=CJFDN0911&filename=DDCP201101003&urlid=&yx=&v=MDU3MDVyRzRIOURNcm85Rlo0UjhlWDFMdXhZUzdEaDFUM3FUcldNMUZyQ1VSTCtmWnVScUZ5RGhXN3pNSVNuSWY= 《官有病，天知否》] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304223812/http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=2&CurRec=2&dbcode=CJFD&dbname=CJFDN0911&filename=DDCP201101003&urlid=&yx=&v=MDU3MDVyRzRIOURNcm85Rlo0UjhlWDFMdXhZUzdEaDFUM3FUcldNMUZyQ1VSTCtmWnVScUZ5RGhXN3pNSVNuSWY= |date=2016-03-04 }}</ref>。湖南[[双峰县|双峰县]]人，现居[[长沙|长沙]]。重要文学期刊《当代》杂志发表过《官病》等长篇小说<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://epub.cnki.net/kns/oldNavi/n_Catalog.aspx?NaviID=1&YearID=DDCP201101&BaseID=DDCP&Field=%e6%8b%bc%e9%9f%b3%e5%88%8a%e5%90%8d*%e5%b9%b4*%e6%9c%9f&Value=DDCP*2011*01&NaviLink=%e5%bd%93%e4%bb%a3(%e9%95%bf%e7%af%87%e5%b0%8f%e8%af%b4%e9%80%89%e5%88%8a)-%2fkns%2foldNavi%2fn_item.aspx%3fNaviID%3d1%26BaseID%3dDDCP |title=《当代》长篇小说选刊2010年第1期目录 |access-date=2015-01-24 |archive-date=2017-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305001350/http://epub.cnki.net/kns/oldNavi/n_Catalog.aspx?NaviID=1&YearID=DDCP201101&BaseID=DDCP&Field=%e6%8b%bc%e9%9f%b3%e5%88%8a%e5%90%8d*%e5%b9%b4*%e6%9c%9f&Value=DDCP*2011*01&NaviLink=%e5%bd%93%e4%bb%a3(%e9%95%bf%e7%af%87%e5%b0%8f%e8%af%b4%e9%80%89%e5%88%8a)-%2fkns%2foldNavi%2fn_item.aspx%3fNaviID%3d1%26BaseID%3dDDCP |dead-url=no }}</ref>，出版过《[[赶尸|赶尸]]笔记》、《老爷子》、《官疗》等畅销小说与历史人物传记《湘军之父[[罗泽南|罗泽南]]》。作品被耶鲁大学、澳大利亚国家图书馆等学术机构收藏。小说屡屡被盗版印刷或盗用<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2010-11-12/220418359656s.shtml |title=新书出版5天惨被盗版 《[[赶尸|赶尸]]笔记》作者呼吁抵制 |access-date=2015-01-24 |archive-date=2015-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128114728/http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2010-11-12/220418359656s.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其中《赶尸笔记》出版5天即发现盗版。是第一个以个人名义起诉[[百度文库|百度文库]]侵权并获赔的作家<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cqcb.com/cbnews/instant/2011-06-08/1302512.html |title=“百度文库门”获赔第一人朱金泰再发律师函维权 |access-date=2015-01-24 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923210937/http://www.cqcb.com/cbnews/instant/2011-06-08/1302512.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，也是第一个起诉美国[[苹果公司|苹果公司]]侵权的中国作家<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.caixin.com/2012-01-06/100346586.html |title=Chinese Writers Sue Apple for Copyright Violations |access-date=2015-01-25 |archive-date=2017-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170127211956/http://english.caixin.com/2012-01-06/100346586.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hn.rednet.cn/c/2011/06/28/2298733.htm |title=双峰作家朱金泰将起诉苹果App shopper侵权 |access-date=2015-01-24 |archive-date=2015-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128132048/http://hn.rednet.cn/c/2011/06/28/2298733.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

